==Unaffiliated Lutheran denominations== The following denominations are not members of the LWF, ILC, CELC or Global Forum, though several of them work with or are in fellowship with individual members of those associations. In addition, a number of these denominations have fellowship agreements with one another, without being part of any larger association. Note that several of these denominations have congregations in multiple countries. In such cases, the denomination is listed under the country in which its headquarters is located. {|class="wikitable sortable" !Country!!Church body!!Year founded!!Members{{efn-ua|name=Membership}}!!class="unsortable"|Ref |- |{{flag|Angola}}||[[Lutheranism in Angola#Confessional Lutheran Church in Angola|Confessional Lutheran Church in Angola]]{{efn-ua|name=LCMS}}||--||--||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lcms.org/worldwide-regions/africa/angola|title=Angola|website=The Lutheran Church—Missouri Synod|access-date=March 29, 2018}}</ref> |- |{{flag|Australia}}||[[Australian Evangelical Lutheran Church]]||1992||--||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.knightgeorge.info/files/Chronicle%20of%20events%20connected%20with%20the%20AELC%201992-2002.pdf|title=Chronicle of Events Connected with the AELC, 1992-2002|format=pdf|website=The Order of Knight George|access-date=March 12, 2018}}</ref> |- |{{flag|Australia}}||[[Evangelical Lutheran Congregations of the Reformation]]||1966||--||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://elcr.org.au/about/history/|title= How and Why the ELCR Was Formed|website=Evangelical Lutheran Congregations of the Reformation|access-date=April 5, 2018}}</ref> |- |{{flag|Benin}}||[[Evangelical Lutheran Church of Benin]]{{efn-ua|name=LCMS}}||1997||--||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lcms.org/worldwide-regions/africa/benin|title=Benin|website=The Lutheran Church—Missouri Synod|access-date=March 29, 2018}}</ref> |- |{{flag|Burundi}}||[[Evangelical Lutheran Church in Burundi]]{{efn-ua|name=LCMS}}||1997||1,800||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lcm